        <mxCell id="RjiAtdgYc3UGIVJFkeS_-52" value="* apply&amp;nbsp;asynchronous processing&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; -&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;system will avoid congestion from having to receive a sudden high volume of bids and will process them gradually afterward&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;* split dependency between service and DB&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;scenario of 100K request &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;queue handle 10 request/second -&amp;gt; too low&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;need optimize : batching request + multi api from DB to handle more requests in a time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;race condition in a auction item because of event routing random to worker&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;transaction waiting due to lock&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt; one product handle by one worker (subscription/partition)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;explode&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of request usually happen in a product item&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt;routing item to a handle by a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;specific worker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;dashed=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1700" y="-10" width="400" height="290" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
