        <mxCell id="n_pm8QwKcL_X4zQhlUrS-8" value="&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;SSTable(sorted string table)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;div&gt;In segment file. sequence of key-value required sort in key and each ket appear just one time( compaction &amp;amp; merging ensure that)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+&amp;nbsp;benefits&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;*&amp;nbsp;range query becomes more possible&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* merging become more simple and effective&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* not nessesery to keep all key in &lt;b style=&quot;text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;index of segment&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp; instead we use &lt;u&gt;sparse index&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt; optimize space of memory&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=LDFComicSans;" vertex="1" parent="1">
