        <mxCell id="n_pm8QwKcL_X4zQhlUrS-13" value="&lt;u&gt;Memtable&lt;/u&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ maintaining a sorted structure in memory easy than disk&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ size of memtable grow larger gradually -&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;write&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* change to immutable and write to disk as a SSTable file&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;*&amp;nbsp;create new empty one for new incoming write&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;read&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* first searching in memtable&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* second find in most recent SStable file ( each SStable file also have a memory index)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=LDFComicSans;" vertex="1" parent="1">
