        <mxCell id="n_pm8QwKcL_X4zQhlUrS-46" value="&lt;b&gt;&amp;gt;=1 : non-verlap,&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;if a level-L file overlaps only part of a level-(L+1) file, the entire file at level-(L+1) is used as an input to the compaction which&amp;nbsp;will be discarded after the compaction" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;fontFamily=LDFComicSans;" vertex="1" parent="1">
