        <mxCell id="n_pm8QwKcL_X4zQhlUrS-51" value="* lists the set of sorted SSTables on each level&lt;div&gt;* store&amp;nbsp;file’s name and the key range each SST file&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;fontFamily=LDFComicSans;" vertex="1" parent="1">
